        (1053, '2019-06-11 14:17:03.143000', 'the Department of Genetics at Harvard Medical School houses a faculty working on diverse problems, using a variety of approaches and model organisms, and having a unified focus on the genome as an organizing principle for understanding biological phenomena.', 'https://genetics.hms.harvard.edu/', '2023-04-11 09:48:33.227000', 'Department of Genetics, Harvard Medical School, Boston, Massachusetts', 'US', null),
